    h1 Timeline
    ul.docs-index
    p Framework7 comes with Timeline component that allows to display both Vertical & Horizontal timeline layouts.
    .with-device
      h2(data-device-preview="../docs-demos/core/timeline-vertical.html") Vertical Timeline
      p Common Vertical Timeline layout could be treated as the following:
      :code(lang="html")
            &lt;div class="timeline"&gt;
              &lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
                &lt;div class="timeline-item-date"&gt;21 &lt;small&gt;DEC&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;div class="timeline-item-divider"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;div class="timeline-item-content"&gt;
                  &lt;div class="timeline-item-inner"&gt;
                    &lt;div class="timeline-item-time"&gt;12:30&lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="timeline-item-title"&gt;Title&lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="timeline-item-subtitle"&gt;Subtitle&lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="timeline-item-text"&gt;Text&lt;/div&gt;
                  &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
                ... another timeline item ...
              &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
      p Where
      ul
        li <code>timeline</code> - main timeline wrapping element. Required
          ul
            li <code>timeline-item</code> - single timeline item. Required
              ul
                li <code>timeline-item-date</code> - timeline item date. Required
                li <code>timeline-item-divider</code> - timeline item decorative divider. Required for vertical timeline
                li <code>timeline-item-content</code> - timeline item content wrapping. You can put any content here: text, cards, list block, custom HTML or special temeline elements. Required
                  ul
                    li <code>timeline-item-inner</code> - item content additional decorative wrapping. Optional
                    li <code>timeline-item-time</code> - item time. Optional
                    li <code>timeline-item-title</code> - item title. Optional
                    li <code>timeline-item-subtitle</code> - item subtitle. Optional
                    li <code>timeline-item-text</code> - item text. Optional
