      h3(data-device-preview="../docs-demos/core/timeline-vertical-sides.html") Vertical Timeline Side By Side
      p There is another "side-by-side" mode available for Vertical Timeline where each next item will be on different side. To enable "side-by-side" mode you need to add <code>timeline-sides</code> class to main <code>timeline</code> element. It is also possible to enable this mode only for tablet devices by adding <code>tablet-sides</code> class to main timeline element.
      p To force timeline element to required side we may use additional <code>timeline-item-left</code> and <code>timeline-item-right</code> classes on single timeline item element <code>timeline-item</code>
      :code(lang="html")
