      h2(data-device-preview="../docs-demos/core/timeline-horizontal.html") Horizontal Timeline
      p Horizontal Timeline has the same layout as Vertical but witha addional <code>timeline-horizontal</code> class on main <code>timeline</code> element.
      p We can also control columns per view in timeline by using <a href="grid.html">Layout Grid</a> columns' classes like <code>col-33</code> and <code>tablet-20</code> (to define column width for large tablet screens).
      :code(lang="html")
            &lt;!--
            Additional "timeline-horizontal" class to enable Horizontal timeline
            Additional "col-50" to define column width (50%)
            Additional "tablet-20" to define column width for tablets (20%)
            --&gt;
            &lt;div class="timeline timeline-horizontal col-50 tablet-20"&gt;
              &lt;!-- Timeline Item (Day) --&gt;
              &lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
                &lt;div class="timeline-item-date"&gt;21 &lt;small&gt;DEC&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
